{"tid":790821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江溫州發生非洲豬瘟疫情 340頭豬死亡","createTime":"2018-08-23T10:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T10:32:28.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5fdf67c923a6c578f990ba052449af7f6eb91e","tid":790821,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"大陸農業農村部23日發布消息指出，浙江溫州市樂清市發生一起非洲豬瘟疫情。某養殖小區3個養殖戶的生豬出現不明原因死亡。截至目前，發病430頭，死亡340頭。<br />\n <br />\n8月22日，經中國動物衛生與流行病學中心確診，為非洲豬瘟疫情。目前，疫情已得到有效處置。"},{"pid":"bfd33626b99ddf51da5f1f57b3fe90b18189e483","tid":790821,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"報出黎430,真實。。。。。"},{"pid":"d33d0847d2209510d6fd7c8bd12869a5a87de0ab","tid":790821,"uid":39320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"没事儿"},{"pid":"2e58013aa6127b07d95fa0a2f3bde0a2e38f11ea","tid":790821,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"瘟州"},{"pid":"841b8a2717efd3525cd301b5f04e1af364dfdc5e","tid":790821,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"又死定之前嗰單？"},{"pid":"59aadd6ddb4d0ac24d0e19ecdd33410678cbec05","tid":790821,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cf470b39f6a6dd0585000602ad7cabd3633afee","tid":790821,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"好快就到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/182906_1291988cf84379c179e5bbe9bd706431.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F182906_1291988cf84379c179e5bbe9bd7